
  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      padding: 24px;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    "
  >
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">

      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for signing up for <strong>Escapeasy</strong>.
      </p>

      <p style="text-align:justify">
        To complete your registration, please verify your email address by
        clicking the button below:
      </p>

      <a
        href="{{VerificationLink}}"
        style="
          display: inline-block;
          margin: 24px 0;
          padding: 12px 20px;
          background-color: #4c74b1;
          color: #ffffff;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: bold;
          border-radius: 4px;
        "
      >
        Verify Email Address
      </a>

      <p style="text-align:justify">
        Once verified, you can start browsing properties and managing your
        escape bookings on Escapeasy.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666666;">
        This verification link will expire in <strong>one hour</strong>.
        If you did not create an account, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>

      <p>
        Kind regards,<br />
        <strong>The Escapeasy Team</strong>
      </p>
      <h2 style="color: #4c74b1; margin-bottom: 14px;">
        Escapeasy.
      </h2>
      
       <hr style="margin: 32px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;" />

      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888888;">
        Need help? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:{{SupportEmail}}" style="color: #3f2f2a;">
          {{SupportEmail}}
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
